/*Using any combination of the other vertical align properties appears to increase the line height and break vertical rhythm. The following appears to achieve the desired visual affect without the line-height issuehttp://spaceninja.com/2009/09/how-to-avoid-paragraph-gaps-when-using-superscript-and-subscript/ */sub,sup {	font-size : .85em;	line-height : 0;	position : relative;	vertical-align : baseline}sub {	bottom : -.33em}sup {	bottom : .33em}